text: Viačasław Francavič Kiebič ( , ; 10 June 1936 – 9 December 2020) was a Belarusian politician. He was the 1st Prime Minister of Belarus from 1991 to 1994. Kebich died on 9 December 2020 at a hospital in Minsk, Belarus from COVID-19, aged 84.Умер Вячеслав Кебич.
